# The fragment and algorithm bundlers embed source bytes verbatim into committed generated
# artifacts, and the freshness guard hashes those artifacts, so a CRLF checkout would rebuild
# to a different hash and fail the gate on an untouched tree. LF everywhere keeps a build
# reproducible regardless of a contributor's core.autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.mp4 binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.wasm binary
